nd的AlphaFold诞生五年来，取得的一系列重大科研突破。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165786\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.95\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"1530\" data-height=\"1454\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=022f3957&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdribvOG7yVybmbOBGHYondqehVtEj4zFosibG8BSZicZ6G3CPGibkgAgmmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u127\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，谷歌DeepMind也将纪录片《思维游戏》（</span></span><em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">The Thinking Game</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">）发布在YouTube。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165782\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8037037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"1170\" data-height=\"940\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"452\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f329f4b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdeJVBvXoyR9XuECkNx3vYiandnWrwyYlSjebHQTwsniaYIiczop0GUdxOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1r3v\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mijl0713mf9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">DeepMind官推</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijn1pq0x6l\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mijn1pq514cr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">纪录片《思维游戏》第一部分</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u19mz\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mijl0cjd1229\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">纪录片《思维游戏》第二部分</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1mqb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是一个关于等待与顿悟的故事，也是生物学在过去五年经历的缩影。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">寻找那把丢失的钥匙</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u11yj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在维也纳分子病理学研究所，生化学家安德烈娅·保利（Andrea Pauli）曾陷入长达十年的困惑。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165783\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.665314401622718\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"493\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"493\" data-height=\"328\" data-backw=\"493\" data-backh=\"328\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86e00aea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdg3S0icZTRwGR0h0QMfbczYo0pHCSlOfTZtcMh1b66JkVrib0jdMy3BCg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u19de\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了搞清楚精子和卵子究竟是如何「相遇」的，她在2018年就在斑马鱼的卵子表面发现了一种至关重要的蛋白质，她给它起名叫「Bouncer」（保镖）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1tod\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个名字很形象，因为如果没有它，受精过程根本不会发生。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u14ms\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但问题在于，这位「保镖」到底是如何识别并放行精子的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1od0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">保利的团队和世界各地的同行们苦苦思索，试图在显微镜下通过无数次生化实验解开这个分子层面的「握手」机制，却始终找不到那把钥匙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1ihz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">直到2020年11月，一场海啸从伦敦的DeepMind实验室呼啸而来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1xy\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">AlphaFold 2横空出世。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5uboj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个AI系统以惊人的精度预测出了蛋白质的三维结构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1wpq\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">那一刻，原本模糊的微观世界突然变得清晰可见。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1r0j\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于保利来说，这就像是在黑暗的房间里突然开了一盏灯：AlphaFold迅速预测出了一种名为Tmem81的精子蛋白结构，它能与另外两个蛋白形成复合物，恰好构建出一个完美的「口袋」，让「Bouncer」得以嵌入结合。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165787\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6401564537157758\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"767\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"767\" data-height=\"491\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"360\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d406bbf1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdWLAZQL88bEshL08Vtel7x1N3icu5iadkzE3I42KzfMelib481UontzzOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijn3ewn1h3q\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mijn3ews1wvc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Tmem81的AlphaFold模型</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u6kg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">困扰人类十年的生殖谜题，被AI在几分钟内破解了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1e35\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验随后验证了这一切。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u20xg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，保利感慨道：「它加速了所有的发现。现在我们每一个项目都在用它。」</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">结构生物学的「第二次降临」</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u18o\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一幕，只是AlphaFold五周岁生日之际，全球无数实验室里的一个缩影。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5uoc8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">把日历翻回五年前的那个深秋，当DeepMind揭开AlphaFold 2的面纱时，科学界感受到的是巨大的冲击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1hj8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说2018年的第一代版本还只是「令人感兴趣」，那么第二代版本则直接展现了「统治力」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u4d2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它生成的3D模型在许多情况下已经与耗资昂贵的实验图谱难以区分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1hou\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">欧洲生物信息学研究所（EMBL-EBI）的生物信息学家珍妮特·桑顿（Janet Thornton）用了一个极具宗教色彩的比喻来形容这场变革：「拥有了预测万物的模型，其影响是巨大的。这就像是结构生物学的“第二次降临”（Second Coming）。」</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165784\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1280\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c28478e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAd4T8uDEkghYRd5ibk6DsCiaX5GMhtA91jFe2RuM2LYjJiazGtGLVa2BicfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1rck\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一变革的烈度，量化在数据里是惊人的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5uz6v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">自2021年关于AlphaFold 2的论文在《自然》杂志发表以来，短短几年间，它已被引用了近4万次。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505165792\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.31851851851851853\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-width=\"1456\" data-height=\"464\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"179\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35b85718&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAd3ysDCiaYCtK0Oxxq1f7SmvJGeBoZTicRArpcfbcibxQicL2afxr7JZuHgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1mzu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">与许多在热点过去后关注度就断崖式下跌的研究不同，AlphaFold的热度曲线是一条昂扬向上的直线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u24on\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">更重要的是，DeepMind做出了一个决定：他们将其代码开源，并与EMBL-EBI合作建立了数据库。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"306\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1002\" data-imgfileid=\"505165791\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1836\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=88fa07d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdxoUbPIYCWlJkkUqNpN5o4l2dnwqRmic6ZsIA1DHA33rp9fkGnM38Ehw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D9\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u8i7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个数据库如今像是一个不断膨胀的宇宙，包含了超过2.4亿个预测结构，几乎囊括了人类已知的所有蛋白质。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1a8u\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">全球190个国家的330万名研究人员涌入这里，其中超过100万用户来自中国、印度等中低收入国家。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"321\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"429\" data-imgfileid=\"505165788\" data-ratio=\"0.5712383488681758\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"751\" data-width=\"751\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e92234bf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdRAm9jLTEqHD4ALhoEoPfIpyCYAxAcvvDhCmUL9GrRJ3IRsgekxVFWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D10\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5utl4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这不仅是技术的胜利，更是科学平权的胜利——无论是在哈佛的顶级实验室，还是在发展中国家的大学宿舍，只要有一根网线，你就能看见生命的精密蓝图。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">从预测结构到重塑科学</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u17ad\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">2024年，AlphaFold的缔造者德米斯·哈萨比斯（Demis Hassabis）约翰·詹珀（John Jumper）分享了诺贝尔化学奖的一半殊荣。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"432\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"970\" data-imgfileid=\"505165789\" data-ratio=\"0.7694444444444445\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1260\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c92f207a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdnIRVBxhchhoISRfvccaL6EIDYz3ZckUAwh5P6N2ic5TQLl8zK7cpZBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D12\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u9sn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这对于一个诞生仅五年的工具来说，几乎是光速的认可。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1woo\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但詹珀本人关注的却是另一个问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1ict\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">看着像保利这样的科学家利用AlphaFold做出的突破，他不仅感到骄傲，更在好奇：「什么时候会有人因为「使用」AlphaFold而赢得那些大奖呢？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u67z\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这绝非随口说出的空话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u4eh\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一份由DeepMind资助的研究发现，使用AlphaFold的研究人员向PDB（蛋白质数据库）提交的实验结构数量，比未使用该工具的同行多出了约50%。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin:0px 8px 24px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"296\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"395\" data-imgfileid=\"505165790\" data-ratio=\"0.525965379494008\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"751\" data-width=\"751\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74014d22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0UGaiciaAGMAs69EFn4rxGAdOkdibuxZw8hSnn0SJJR3RSiaSpHZkaYIoFwmRREQEK4WSfdWVTomHT4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D13\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u238u\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这揭示了一个现象：AI并没有像某些人担心的那样「取代」实验学家，反而在「反哺」他们。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5umj7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">那些通过X射线晶体学或冷冻电镜得到的模糊原始数据，因为有了AI预测结构的辅助，变得更容易解读。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1r99\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">詹珀说：「我喜欢这种感觉，它帮助了那些最初为我们提供数据的人。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u242k\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这形成了一个完美的闭环：人类的实验数据训练了AI，AI反过来帮助人类看清实验数据，进而产生更多的数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1s1t\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这场循环中，科学发现的齿轮被按下了快进键。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1zq8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">五年过去，AlphaFold已经不再是一个单纯的新闻热词，它变成了像移液枪、显微镜一样的科研「基建」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u22ev\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它悄无声息地融入了每一篇论文的致谢里，融入了每一次药物设计的构想中，融入了人类对生命最本质奥秘的每一次凝视。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: justify;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5uk6h\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在原子与代码的交响中，人类终于不再只是在黑暗中摸索生命的形状，而是点亮了一盏灯，看清了造物主留下的每一行诗句。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u6ia\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mijn4denyjt\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijn4den15pn\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-03886-9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-03886-9</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mijmph5u1zoa\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mijn4den1d\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d95J8yzvjbQ\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d95J8yzvjbQ</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章回顾了谷歌 DeepMind 的 AlphaFold 诞生五年来的里程碑成就，通过案例展示其在蛋白质结构预测领域的革命性影响，并探讨其如何加速科学发现、促进科学平权。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章回顾了谷歌 DeepMind 的 AlphaFold 诞生五年来的里程碑成就，通过案例展示其在蛋白质结构预测领域的革命性影响，并探讨其如何加速科学发现、促进科学平权。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了谷歌 DeepMind 的 AlphaFold 在过去五年中对结构生物学领域产生的深远影响。通过生化学家 Andrea Pauli 十年未解的“精卵结合”分子机制被 AlphaFold 几分钟内破解的案例，生动展现了 AlphaFold 预测蛋白质三维结构的强大能力。文章指出，AlphaFold 的出现被誉为结构生物学的“第二次降临”，其相关论文被引用近 4 万次，且 DeepMind 将其代码开源并建立了包含超 2.4 亿个预测结构的数据库，极大地促进了全球科学研究的平权和加速。文章还提及 AlphaFold 的缔造者获得诺贝尔化学奖，并强调 AI 并非取代实验学家，而是通过辅助实验数据解读，形成人类与 AI 协同加速科学发现的良性循环，使 AlphaFold 成为科研的“基建”工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
